      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个展示双向合并流程的Git图，重点是从底部往顶部发展的视角。标题就叫\"Two-way merges (bottom-to-top)\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
