        "gitGraph BT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，BT方向就是从下往上生长。那我先画一个main分支的起点commit，然后分出一个develop分支，这样开始可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "branch",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，develop切出来后先做一个commit，然后切回main去merge develop，这是第一次合并。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一次合并完成了。接下来develop要再merge main，然后develop上再做一个commit，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge main",
        "commit",
        "develop"
