      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，顺序需要调整一下——develop merge main之后，应该先切回main，最后再由main来merge develop，形成完整的双向循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop",
        "two-way merges"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，所以完整的流程是：main←develop→main←develop，两次交叉合并。我检查一下，develop上的commit是在第二次merge main之前还是之后？",
      "elements_involved": [
